22
00:01:00,750 --> 00:01:01,890
And that is impressive,

23
00:01:01,890 --> 00:01:05,590
given the Communist Party’s decades of propaganda

24
00:01:05,590 --> 00:01:08,110
about how terrible the Japanese are.

25
00:01:08,110 --> 00:01:09,480
But don’t worry,

26
00:01:09,480 --> 00:01:11,690
there’s still something the Chinese Communist
Party

27
00:01:11,690 --> 00:01:14,340
can hate even more than Japan.

28
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:16,800
And that is America.

29
00:01:16,800 --> 00:01:19,580
China’s Foreign Ministry is accusing the
US

30
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:22,360
of not helping with the coronavirus

31
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:25,550
and spreading fear and chaos by…

32
00:01:25,550 --> 00:01:29,260
...evacuating its citizens from Wuhan.

33
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:34,140
And instituting a travel ban on foreign nationals
coming in from China.

34
00:01:34,140 --> 00:01:36,720
Just like many other countries.

35
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:38,930
Including Japan.

36
00:01:38,930 --> 00:01:43,590
And while Chinese state-run media accused
the US of not offering help,

37
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:45,580
that’s...a lie.

38
00:01:45,580 --> 00:01:50,930
The US had offered to send CDC experts to
help in Wuhan.

39
00:01:50,930 --> 00:01:53,000
That was back in early January,

40
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:56,960
when officials were still trying to pretend
things were fine.

41
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:59,650
China rejected the US’s offer.

42
00:01:59,650 --> 00:02:03,870
Now US experts will be joining a W.H.O. delegation

43
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:05,510
to help with the coronavirus.

44
00:02:05,510 --> 00:02:07,620
Meanwhile, the Chinese central government

45
00:02:07,620 --> 00:02:10,320
is demanding that local Wuhan officials

46
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:13,740
round up everyone who may be infected,

47
00:02:13,740 --> 00:02:16,280
and force them to go to quarantine centers.

48
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:18,580
A Beijing official has demanded that

49
00:02:18,580 --> 00:02:21,390
“City investigators should go to each home

50
00:02:21,390 --> 00:02:24,850
to check the temperatures of every resident.”

51
00:02:24,850 --> 00:02:28,350
And that “During these wartime conditions,

52
00:02:28,350 --> 00:02:29,820
there must be no deserters,

53
00:02:29,820 --> 00:02:35,430
or they will be nailed to the pillar of historical
shame forever.”

54
00:02:35,430 --> 00:02:37,790
It should be noted that the quarantine centers

55
00:02:37,790 --> 00:02:42,000
don’t actually have nearly enough beds for
everyone.

56
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:45,600
And many of them don’t have enough doctors
or supplies

57
00:02:45,600 --> 00:02:50,280
or even basic conditions to prevent the spread
of infection.

58
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:53,230
Although mentioning that might also get you

59
00:02:53,230 --> 00:02:55,860
nailed to that pillar of historical shame.

60
00:02:55,860 --> 00:02:59,170
Here’s a photo from inside a Wuhan gymnasium

61
00:02:59,170 --> 00:03:02,540
that’s being converted into a quarantine
center.

62
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:06,530
That does not look like a good isolation ward
to me.

63
00:03:06,530 --> 00:03:11,140
And anyone trying to get real news out from
Wuhan is being targeted.

64
00:03:11,140 --> 00:03:13,730
One citizen journalist named Fang Bin spent
days

65
00:03:13,730 --> 00:03:15,650
